data.description: With over 2,700 square feet, this new home design offers the space and storage you want. The extended foyer leads to an open concept kitchen and family room plus a formal dining room highlighted by dramatic arches. A private bedroom and full bath complete the main level. Upstairs features a spacious owner's getaway with separate sitting room and spa-like bath. Secondary bedrooms have lots of natural light plus a shared Jack and Jill bath. A versatile loft provides additional living space for movie nights, entertaining and recreation. Click the RED REQUEST INFO box for more information! Photos used for illustrative purposes and do not depict actual home.
